(55, 1, 5, 2, NULL, '000031908470', 'BRAZILIAN NATURAL SMOOTHING', '0', NULL, 110.00, 20.00, 100, 'Smoothing treatment, without formaldehyde, with a professional result, which restores and recovers the strength of the hair, thanks to its improved formula with Argan Oil, Shea Butter, Vegetable Keratin, Amino Acids and Glyoxylic, which penetrates the hair strand by smoothing it up to 12 weeks\r\nRecovers the strength of the hair and restores shine, hydration and softness; leaving it manageable and with natural movement\r\n\r\nBENEFITS :\r\nSmooth hair with curls, waves, volume and frizz.\r\nRecover strength, shine, hydration and softness ..\r\nProfessional result for up to 12 weeks.\r\nEliminate volume and frizz.\r\nNo formaldehyde, no guanidine, no toxic vapors.\r\nWith thermal protection and thermal memory: smoothing is activated by the heat of the dryer.\r\nRESULT.\r\nStraighter, soft and shiny hair, with natural movement.\r\n\r\nHOW TO USE :\r\nStep 1 : Wash the hair with Pre Treatment Shampoo, then dry it completely with a towel and dryer. Conditioner should not be applied after shampoo.\r\n\r\nStep 2 : Once clean and completely dry, divide the hair into 4 zones, start the application of the straightening mask by one of the 2 areas on the back of the head. Apply the product, wick per wick (1 to 1 cm wide), leaving  cm from the root, making sure to cover all the hair in a homogeneous way. Make sure the mask covers all the hair. Leave on for 15 minutes and, after the time, remove the excess product, if any, with the help of a comb.\r\n\r\nStep 3 : Proceed to dry the hair with the help of a dryer and a brush (flat, round or comb), in a downward direction and without brushing to avoid the removal of the product, until leaving the hair completely dry.\r\n\r\nStep 4 : Iron all hair using thin strands, pass the iron 8 to 12 times at a temperature between 200  C and 230  C (392  F to 446  F). Make sure that after ironing there is no residue of the Brazilian Smoothing mask. Before starting the next step, wait 5 minutes.\r\n\r\nIMPORTANT: In case of very fine or damaged hair, we recommend to quickly pass the iron, especially at the ends of the hair or otherwise lower the temperature of the hair to 150  C or 180 \r\n\r\nStep 5 : Wash the hair with the Shampoo, apply the Conditioner and rinse. Then, dry the hair naturally or with the help of the dryer\r\n\r\nWARNING FOR DYED HAIRS: This product may cause a variation in hair color. It is recommended to match the date of the next coloring.', '15791782775e205925abb09.jpg', 1, '2020-01-16 19:37:57', '2020-01-16 19:37:57'),
